The paper deals with communication strategies for a wireless sensor network scenario, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of feedback in the multiple access channel also suggests a systems and control perspective (cs.SY). The paper also involves numerical computations on Gaussian channels, which could fall under machine learning (cs.MM) or learning theory (cs.LG).
